race.description: Av Stone Marble & Granite Mobile Pace
race.comment: LETSTACOBOUTIT (4) finished third at this track two starts back, then did a good job again at his latest appearance over 1770m at the same circuit, beaten 14 metres into third after being handy in the run. Meets a comparable field, so he can play a significant role. FLEXI BET (2) finished sixth at this track two runs ago before a comparable effort at her latest appearance over 1770m at this track, beaten 17 metres. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Big chance if things go her way. BETTING ON COURAGE (3) has been about the mark of late and must be respected, the latest offering a sound fifth at Dubbo over 1720m. Each way value. Something for the Multiples: IDEAL TAO (6)
